nodes.text: The Malastare Special Service was an organization on Malastare around 32 BBY. The Special Service posted a bounty on Jenatahza for being a participant in a plot to murder Representative Ainlee Teem. Jango Fett claimed the bounty alive for the Special Service.
The Service also posted a bounty for Tahbotza, for attempted blackmail of Senator Ask Aak's support staff. This bounty was also claimed by Fett.
